data.description: Great opportunity to own a beautiful piece of property with many nice oak trees. Wonderful place for your custom home. Three power poles already exist on this property, saving you thousands of dollars. Ag exemption is already in place as well. This property is tucked away and has nice privacy, but is only minutes from town. Bertram Woods subdivision offers connection to the community water well once for each owner/tract of land or you may drill your own well.
